### Text content
All section H2 titles and description paragraphs use `[Content TBD]` as placeholder text. The agent must not invent or hallucinate descriptions. Example:
```
<h2>[Content TBD — section title]</h2>
<p>[Content TBD — section description]</p>
```

## Scope Contracts

### Scope Contract 1: Page Structure + FeatureSection Component

**UX Slice**
- User sees long page with 14 clearly separated sections
- Each section has an H2 title placeholder and one-line description placeholder

**Architecture Slice**
- `sanglogium.astro`: 14 `<section>` elements with semantic `id` attributes per the section list above
- `FeatureSection.astro`: `title`, `description`, `reversed` props; desktop `grid-cols-2`, `flex-row-reverse` when `reversed`; mobile `flex-col`
- Sections 10 (auth) and 13 (images) use special visual slots (code block / SVG) — pass different slot content, same component
- `scroll-margin-top: 5rem` applied to all `<section>` elements

**Human Verification Checklist**
- [ ] All 14 sections visible on page
- [ ] Each section has an H2 placeholder and description placeholder (no invented content)
- [ ] Desktop: two-column layout, alternating sides per section
- [ ] Mobile: single column, visual above text

---

### Scope Contract 2: Screenshots + Astro Image Optimization

**UX Slice**
- 12 sections show placeholder images (all sections with screenshot slots)
- Images load lazily except the hero

**Architecture Slice**
- Astro `<Image>` component for sections 2–9, 11–12, 14 (12 sections)
- Placeholder PNGs from `src/assets/images/sanglogium/`
- Hero (section 1): `loading="eager" fetchpriority="high"`
- All other images: `loading="lazy"`

**Human Verification Checklist**
- [ ] 12 sections show images; no broken image links
- [ ] Below-fold images load on scroll (check Network tab — not loaded on page load)
- [ ] `astro build` generates `.webp` or `.avif` variants in `dist/`

