### Scope Contract 3: Auth Section (Code Block) + Image Pipeline (Diagram)

**UX Slice**
- Auth section shows a formatted code block instead of a screenshot
- Image Pipeline section shows the placeholder SVG diagram

**Architecture Slice**
- Auth: `<pre><code>` block in the visual slot of `FeatureSection`; content is a short placeholder code snippet (e.g. a simple TypeScript auth check); horizontal scroll on mobile if needed (`overflow-x: auto`)
- Image Pipeline: `<img>` referencing `src/assets/images/sanglogium/images-pipeline-diagram.svg` in the visual slot

**Human Verification Checklist**
- [ ] Auth section shows a formatted code block, not an image
- [ ] Image Pipeline section shows the SVG diagram
- [ ] Both are readable on mobile (code block has horizontal scroll if needed)

